OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with some late
OL,7,Fhazy sunshine. The rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be predominately dry with clear
OL,9,Fspells, but a few showers possible
OL,10,Facross Upper Tayside.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA bright morning with hazy
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Cloud will tend to
OL,14,Fdevelop through the day and bring a
OL,15,Ffew showers, some of which may be on
OL,16,Fthe heavy side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
