OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA good
OL,6,Fdeal of dry weather during this period
OL,7,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
OL,8,FHowever a few showers or spells of
OL,9,Frain can't be ruled out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
